Seapro 4 Stroke

Engine Details

The new Mercury 300hp SeaPro™ four-stroke outboards provide what you demand to get the job done – plenty of displacement, power, efficiency and durability. The impressive muscle of our new V8 4.6-liter powerheads is specifically designed for commercial duty and delivers our best-ever fuel economy. The one-two combination of ample torque and low weight makes these engines ideal for heavily loaded boats. Advanced Range Optimization (ARO) and closed-loop fuel control work together to precisely adjust the fuel mixture for optimal fuel economy. For commercial workboats and law-enforcement boats.
